% this file tests comments, text/code/eval fragments and constant definitions
This is text
% this is a LaTeX comment
\begin{flalign*}
&\text{Define}~a : \mathbb{N}~\text{by}&\\
&a = 0.&
\end{flalign*}
more text
\begin{flalign*}
&\text{Define}~b : \mathbb{N}~\text{by}&\\
&b = a.&
\end{flalign*}
And now we use evaluation to determine $a = 0$ and $b = 0$.

We can also just do arbitrary expressions, like evaluating $\lfloor\sqrt{11}\rfloor + 5 = 8$.